summary: “Not sure if you picked up on it yet. I’m pretty sure you have though. Have you noticed that you have a light-up bracelet on...
caption: “Not sure if you picked up on it yet. I’m pretty sure you have though. Have you noticed that you have a light-up bracelet on your wrist? (…) The reason why I wanted to have these on the tour is because this is actually my very first all-stadium tour, which has been so much fun because of you. So, one thing you know about stadiums is they’re just massive places to play, I wanted to make sure that no matter what, I could see every single one of you in these stadiums.”
